commit 24f1cf432e89dbbb69577d7de527a86e229588d5
Author: Mike Laiosa <mike@laiosa.org>
Date:   Fri May 17 08:51:01 2013 -0700

    Remove DOCTYPE from the plist XML.
    
    Remove DOCTYPE from the plist XML before feeding it to the parser, so it
    doesn't try to download the DTD.  This speeds things up, and makes it
    more reliable

